{"componentChunkName":"component---node-modules-gatsby-theme-portfolio-minimal-src-templates-article-index-tsx","path":"/my-first-article/python/python2/","result":{"pageContext":{"article":{"banner":{"alt":"파이썬 기초","caption":"Photo by <u><a href=\"https://unsplash.com/photos/Nc5Q_CEcY44\">Google</a></u>","src":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/fe2007ff5fefc27a884eb9773510900b/b87af/pythonlogo.png","srcSet":"/static/fe2007ff5fefc27a884eb9773510900b/ea049/pythonlogo.png 125w,\n/static/fe2007ff5fefc27a884eb9773510900b/bf58b/pythonlogo.png 250w,\n/static/fe2007ff5fefc27a884eb9773510900b/b87af/pythonlogo.png 500w","sizes":"(min-width: 500px) 500px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/fe2007ff5fefc27a884eb9773510900b/df328/pythonlogo.webp 125w,\n/static/fe2007ff5fefc27a884eb9773510900b/2d2c6/pythonlogo.webp 250w,\n/static/fe2007ff5fefc27a884eb9773510900b/01f4a/pythonlogo.webp 500w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 500px) 500px, 100vw"}]},"width":660,"height":399.96}}}},"body":"<h2>자료형</h2>\n<p>자료형이란 프로그래밍 할 때 쓰는 숫자, 문자열 등 자료 형태로 사용하는 모든 것을 뜻한다. 프로그램의 기본이자 핵심 단위사 바로 자료형이다.</p>\n<h3>숫자형</h3>\n<h4>정수형</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>정수형(lnteger)이란 말 그대로 정수를 뜻하는 자료형을 말한다.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\">a_int <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">100</span>\nb_int <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">100</span>\nc_int <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>type()은 파이썬 변수의 타입을 확인해주는 함수이다.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token builtin\">type</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>a_int<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">int</code></pre></div>\n<h4>실수형</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>파이썬에서 실수형(Floating-point)은 소수점이 포함된 숫자를 말한다.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\">t_flo <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">5.12</span>\nY_flo <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">12.0</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token builtin\">type</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>t_flo<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">float</code></pre></div>\n<h5>컴퓨터식 지수 표현방식</h5>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\">a_flo <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">12.789e10</span>\na_flo</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">127890000000.0</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\">b_flo <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">78.456e-4</span>\nb_flo</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">0.0078456</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token builtin\">type</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>a_flo<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">type</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>b_flo<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">(float, float)</code></pre></div>\n<h3>숫자형 연산</h3>\n<h4>사칙연산</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>\"+\" : 더하기</li>\n<li>\"-\" : 빼기</li>\n<li>\"*\" : 곱하기</li>\n<li>\"/\" : 나누기</li>\n<li>\"**\" : 제곱</li>\n<li>\"%\" : 나머지만</li>\n<li>\"//\" : 몫만</li>\n</ul>\n<h5>\"+\" : 더하기</h5>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token comment\"># \"+\" : 더하기</span>\na_int <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">4</span>\nb_int <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">5</span>\na_int <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> b_int </code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">9</code></pre></div>\n<h5>\"-\" : 빼기</h5>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\">a_int <span class=\"token operator\">-</span> b_int</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">-1</code></pre></div>\n<h5>\"*\" : 곱하기</h5>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\">a_int <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> b_int</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">20</code></pre></div>\n<h5>\"/\" : 나누기</h5>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\">a_int <span class=\"token operator\">/</span> b_int</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">0.8</code></pre></div>\n<h5>\"**\" : 제곱</h5>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\">a_int <span class=\"token operator\">**</span> b_int</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">1024</code></pre></div>\n<h5>\"%\" : 나머지만</h5>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\">a_int <span class=\"token operator\">%</span> b_int</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">4</code></pre></div>\n<h5>\"//\" : 몫만</h5>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\">a_int <span class=\"token operator\">//</span> b_int</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">0</code></pre></div>","categories":["Python","기초"],"date":"September 27, 2023","description":"파이썬 기초","id":"3bac473d-788d-56da-aeec-581494357126","keywords":["Python","기초","자료형"],"slug":"/my-first-article/python/python2/","title":"[파이썬 기초] 자료형","readingTime":{"text":"2 min read"}},"listingPagePath":"/blog"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3262260831","948380417"],"slicesMap":{}}